00:01:07.080 --> 00:01:10.880
we realized that we have all
these super cool explorers,

00:01:10.880 --> 00:01:13.430
we have all these
amazing adventure stories,

00:01:13.430 --> 00:01:16.230
we have access to all this
really cool technology.

00:01:16.230 --> 00:01:19.800
