all that stuff and put it

00:01:19.800 --> 00:01:22.340
in a fictional world,
where you guys, the kids,

00:01:22.340 --> 00:01:23.770
are at the center of the action?

00:01:23.770 --> 00:01:25.790
Does that sound cool?

00:01:25.790 --> 00:01:27.750
So, we had this concept.

00:01:27.750 --> 00:01:29.460
And we decided, okay,

00:01:29.460 --> 00:01:31.380
we're going to make
this Explorer Academy.

00:01:31.380 --> 00:01:35.260
