can travel the world on a ship,

00:01:35.260 --> 00:01:39.440
they can dive with whales, they
can uncover ancient artifacts,

00:01:39.440 --> 00:01:42.250
they can scale mountains,
they can scale glaciers.

00:01:42.250 --> 00:01:45.590
And you can basically see
all this amazing planet has

00:01:45.590 --> 00:01:46.910
to offer.

00:01:46.910 --> 00:01:48.860
So, what we needed next
was an author, right?

00:01:48.860 --> 00:01:51.280
You need someone to write it.

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:54.860
So, we had all this cool
stuff, and we needed someone

00:01:54.860 --> 00:01:58.500
