need a bad guy.

00:02:07.860 --> 00:02:10.560
So, there is so many twists and
turns in this story, you guys.

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:13.570
Once you start reading, you
will not be able to stop.

00:02:13.570 --> 00:02:15.670
So, I am so pleased

